description:
hilarious fun, simple, fast-paced free-for-all deathmatch game with tons of unlockable hats!

Super Shape Shooter is an online 2D Mutliplayer Shooter platformer. Choose from three different classes and play in five different maps against your friends and have some gun n jump fun in hilarious epic matches.

Features:

2D Online Multiplayer Shooter
Play against bots or humans
6 different maps
3 different characters
Tons of cosmetic hats to make ur shape unique
